---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Expert Root Canal Treatment in Footscray | Save Your Tooth with Precision Care"
  description="At Top Dentists Footscray, our skilled dentists perform root canal treatments with precision and care to save damaged or infected teeth. We carefully remove infected pulp, clean and disinfect the tooth, and seal it to prevent future infections. Protect your smile with expert root canal therapy that relieves pain and preserves your natural tooth."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Root Canal</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Root Canal Treatment
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              At Top Dentists Footscray, our skilled dentists perform root canal procedures with precision and care. When the soft inner pulp (blood or nerve supply) of a tooth becomes infected through deep decay or injury, root canal treatment may be the best option to save the tooth and prevent the need for extraction.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              This restorative procedure involves removing the damaged or infected pulp, cleaning and disinfecting the inner tooth, and sealing it with a permanent filling material.
            </p>

            <!-- Treatment Process -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                Root Canal Treatment Process
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Diagnosis and examination</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Thorough examination and X-rays to confirm the need for root canal treatment and plan the procedure.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Local anesthesia</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Comfortable numbing of the treatment area to ensure a pain-free procedure.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Pulp removal</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Careful removal of the infected or damaged pulp from inside the tooth.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Cleaning and disinfection</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Thorough cleaning and disinfection of the root canals to eliminate bacteria.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Sealing</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Filling and sealing the root canals with biocompatible material to prevent reinfection.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Benefits of Root Canal Treatment
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Saves Natural Tooth</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Preserves your natural tooth structure instead of extraction</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Pain Relief</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Eliminates infection and associated pain</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Cost-Effective</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">More affordable than tooth replacement options</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Maintains Function</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Preserves normal chewing and biting ability</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Post-Treatment Care -->
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Post-Treatment Care
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                After your root canal procedure, you will receive care instructions to promote healing and longevity of the treated tooth. Good oral hygiene practices, including brushing, flossing, and regular dental visits, will aid in maintaining the life of your root canal treatment.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- When Root Canal is Needed -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Signs You May Need Root Canal Treatment
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Severe toothache when chewing or applying pressure</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Prolonged sensitivity to hot or cold temperatures</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Discoloration of the tooth</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Swelling and tenderness in nearby gums</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Success Rate
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    85-97% Success Rate
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    Root canal treatments have a very high success rate and can last a lifetime with proper care.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Save Your Natural Tooth with Root Canal Treatment
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          Don't let a damaged or infected tooth go untreated. Call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          to learn if root canal therapy is right for you
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>